{"tid":326074,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇咗利物浦訪港 高普記者會 港媒真係冇個掂","createTime":"2017-07-17T16:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T09:28:51.000Z","uid":59408,"like":465,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"824db0dfff11428e74efd8e223a2e3a75bf811ad","tid":326074,"uid":59408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"睇咗利物浦訪港個高普記者會 <br />\n港媒英文真係冇個掂，<br />\n仲要問埋啲無聊嘢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/10155821475312448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F10155821475312448%2F&d=ufi%2FbvJ5JefyUmEdKwOPswHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0f4d2741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/10155821475312448/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港電台<br />\n1. When do expect Liverpool to get the title of Premier League?<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">You have made some comments about the some transfers of Chinese Super League, can you develop more?</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">How</span> do you think about the development of Chinese Super League?<br />\n<br />\n中超Comments 嗰度，高普完全唔知佢問乜！<br />\n問返佢&quot;What comments have I made?&quot; <br />\n原來係講Oscar 單轉會！<br />\n<br />\n一係就How do you see，一係就What do you think about<br />\n你兩個撈埋一齊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHow do you think? 你點諗嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Hi Klopp,</span><br />\n1. You changed the glasses during the summer, <span style=\"color: red;\">is any other players broke your glass again?</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. Why don't you have any social media account? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你想點呀，想Casual 就Hi Jurgen，想嚴肅就Good morning, Mr. Klopp啦！<br />\n想用過去式又講返個 is，glasses 又漏es！<br />\n高普即刻笑柒你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係Did any other players break your glasses again 呀！<br />\n<br />\n有線<br />\nJust want to, how do you see the cost of player becoming higher and higher these years with the cost of the players? How do you see this phenomenon? Will it affect your transfer plan? <span style=\"color: red;\">Like &quot;Kai Walker&quot; is fifth thousand something in pound,</span> is a quite expensive player. Will it, how do you see this phenomenon?<br />\n<br />\n係咁自我重覆！<br />\ncost of the players, cost of the players, <br />\nhow do you see this phenomenon, how do you see this phenomenon<br />\n<br />\nKyle Walker L音完全唔見咗！你就Kai！<br />\n<br />\n五千萬鎊直譯&quot;fifth thousand something in pound&quot; <br />\nWTF? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFifth 定 five 呀？係five thoudsand 喎大佬！<br />\n&quot;萬&quot;譯唔到變咗Something？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFifty Million Pound呀！<br />\n<br />\n前面港台已經問咗Oscar 高價轉會，你又問返同類問題做乜？<br />\n<br />\n明報<br />\n1. After the previous game, you said Salah <span style=\"color: red;\">is like not really don't</span> know how Liverpool defend or how the team work yet, what do you expect from him in HK in these 2 games?<br />\n<br />\n2. You are bringing Danny Ward to HK, <span style=\"color: red;\">the goalkeeper, the young goalkeeper,</span> is he staying in Liverpool for the next season and not like not going on loan to another team is he com enough.<br />\n<br />\n又is 又don't，你又想點？<br />\n一係就Salah doesn't know how Liverpool defend.<br />\n或者Salah is not aware of how Liverpool defend.<br />\n<br />\n你係咪以為高普會突然唔記得咗Danny Ward 呀？<br />\nOK 你想突顯佢後生，你講<br />\nYou are bringing Danny Ward to HK, who is still a young goalkeeper. <br />\n咪得囉！<br />\n仲有，德國男模Karius 同Ward 同年同月同日生㗎！<br />\n咁邊個後生啲呀？你做好功課未呀小姐？<br />\n<br />\n成個記者會，得個渣打高層一個香港人講到完整英文！<br />\n算！唔同你講英文，講做記者！<br />\n<br />\n你哋係訪問緊一個頂級足球教練，<br />\n可能係你體育記者生涯最大嘅一個訪問，<br />\n你哋有好多問題可以問，問埋啲膠嘢？<br />\n蘋果上次問Emma Watson <br />\n&quot;Do you owe Emma Stone a drink?&quot; <br />\n已經出曬醜，柒出國際喇！<br />\n我知港媒要輕鬆搞笑，可唔可平衡返搞笑同認真？<br />\n你哋認真啲喥問題，寫好啲稿得唔得？<br />\n比返啲記者應有水平出嚟可以嘛？<br />\n<br />\n足球戰術，轉會新聞，你唔問都會大把人問，嗰啲交返比外媒啦<br />\n試下問啲外媒唔會問嘅嘢，問啲關於香港嘅嘢得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n我會試下問佢<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港作為細城巿，面對中超崛起，香港足球應該點發展落去？<br />\n你係多仔嗰時，用好少錢就打底拜仁，資源少嘅時候，對球會最重要係乜？香港點先可以同中超鬥呢？<br />\n<br />\n2. 問下佢知唔知香港嘅陳婉婷係全世界第一個女教練贏男子聯賽，<br />\n但係佢今年佢聯賽、亞冠都失利，你執教緬恩思同多仔都面對過好多高低起跌，你會有咩建議比佢呢？<br />\n<br />\n3. 利記咁多年嚟，從來都未有過一位亞洲球員，<br />\n你之前同香川合作過喎，你點睇亞洲球員？<br />\n利記幾時有會第一個亞洲球員？<br />\n<br />\n我知我啲問題都唔係高水準，<br />\n各位巴絲，<br />\n如果比你訪問高普，你會問咩？"},{"pid":"9c48ff8203a83feb6ecf4e638b35f066bd1d9c46","tid":326074,"uid":2313,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:36:19.000Z","msg":"樓豬幾有心，十卜"},{"pid":"0db632eb8108a5e9d7dcc0ce75fcdaf84ac0f96a","tid":326074,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:38:39.000Z","msg":"樓主唔係以前高登個李逍遙呀？"},{"pid":"8015ae5311bc0fcd3d375058779fb117916188c2","tid":326074,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"打咁大篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08029e30cd19124d9d6cb25ccf62372ca7d508d0","tid":326074,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主唔係以前高登個李逍遙呀？</blockquote><br />\n唔係，係迷你嗰個，舊登嗰個唔係我"},{"pid":"388cd6f54fb7ce840872672fd63386aab3793035","tid":326074,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"lm學英文"},{"pid":"b494a474a63c43e3b6d8cfc67ba20e7aae5bd17d","tid":326074,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主做記者啦"},{"pid":"f6d0a2ec2443860e1df4338e076ccd6057d7fc43","tid":326074,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdc24aa1fcfc14c63ec525c08d18385d6ee18c4","tid":326074,"uid":217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"推 比各大垃圾記者睇"},{"pid":"3ff0702b4416bdd2182b471516cb7a4d14dd21f1","tid":326074,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"樓主 英文plz"},{"pid":"6335c9e0ba95698d239eee5326aac032ec70081a","tid":326074,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:44:19.000Z","msg":"正post"},{"pid":"0ad3080255d0ebc17ec72af7bf7eba5f6a44ad49","tid":326074,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"樓主睇黎講中文都唔會錯grandma"},{"pid":"82d1b2aed9ffda3a5865c1804347a10e7f4c839b","tid":326074,"uid":70800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"先唔講英文<br />\n點解香港記者問埋唔關英超問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想搞笑我會問佢羸左英超亞洲杯既通常黎緊果季成績都係唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你有冇信心鸁出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再唔係問佢左閘個缺點仲未解決，黎緊會三線出戰，你有咩方法改善"},{"pid":"9fc4e391918591ecc25d8fa287bb0457365fa315","tid":326074,"uid":44722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"講得好岩<br />\n問埋d垃圾問題<br />\n都唔知係咪體育記者"},{"pid":"fdd964fae50a24de61c7e5843809277226a72aa8","tid":326074,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9dacb0f090dc07851238d71aebe43a47c6b603c","tid":326074,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主睇黎講中文都唔會錯grandma</blockquote><br />\n但係會錯grandpa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3729fa296c0fab1e4b7cfecb4ddf61b88312060","tid":326074,"uid":5191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講得好岩<br />\n問埋d垃圾問題<br />\n都唔知係咪體育記者</blockquote><br />\n有個問幾時贏英超 笑死我"},{"pid":"877acc528fa6410e9923418840bf0e1d2f13f498","tid":326074,"uid":4574,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:49:37.000Z","msg":"成個香港新聞業<br />\n正如老江所講 <br />\ntoo simple sometimes naive"},{"pid":"7a76f32d9077d067ea16ecdf3b0109d4224139d3","tid":326074,"uid":44722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:49:58.000Z","msg":"樓豬問既問題好高汁"},{"pid":"750bfba710f6faa0548f5dcf91c3e5e56f1552a6","tid":326074,"uid":59305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"唔多睇波都入黎留言+正評"},{"pid":"49a2658d3a73f1ec26ddac1396076ff77739c837","tid":326074,"uid":8921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"皮已正<br />\n<br />\n係咪記者太低人工，有料嘅全部都轉哂行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e8725f6138d910f6c1527e25aa398ed04fd4d8","tid":326074,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b45987fde0f694277d439275b9c1562c1553dc4","tid":326074,"uid":63233,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:54:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12eef902f8aa8d384241b9d37b7ec21ffda64a86","tid":326074,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮已正<br />\n<br />\n係咪記者太低人工，有料嘅全部都轉哂行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有料嘅去哂做公關啦"},{"pid":"e6f7f44de744002495a69aa80fd24ced211f28a9","tid":326074,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:55:47.000Z","msg":"而家香港班記者咪淨係識上網抄下其他文當自己寫，source又唔撚check清楚唔知頭唔知路就登出街，嘥鳩氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67da089a1f8e6666665b901114d20b8a20638593","tid":326074,"uid":13088,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"屌晒上面鬧記者既人<br />\n<br />\n上一代班廢老死都唔肯退<br />\n新仔點做啊？<br />\n新仔有知識既邊有機會做呢的位啊<br />\n<br />\n但未講香港體記圍威喂人工低"},{"pid":"ed3ef5af042434ac11a0231f0f26cbe380bcdb0f","tid":326074,"uid":12533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"正評，樓主提出既第三條問題我覺得幾值得問<br />\n而事實上好多記者去訪問之前未必有prep過，同埋無經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108d832c7be38cfa71d1774b169cbc4124979f70","tid":326074,"uid":11311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:03:10.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"2ba3c619ac0913204a6eebc444154df2f82d0461","tid":326074,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:03:34.000Z","msg":"香港記者質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea0f8f4c241f7de827d1bc49d440d54f7d1fbef","tid":326074,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"其實香港重有幾多正職體育記者,唔洗做埋其他組個D?"},{"pid":"d0d47ea5088d39b72bd30886f71c946ceda2c180","tid":326074,"uid":5006,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"體育台難得高質post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55fd0bf5408beb80e5d9396b7c7d4376e828b7a","tid":326074,"uid":6153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a629b115e71d4f6054fec65c2a02778214242a8f","tid":326074,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e05381adfacfe894160c8f5b5b65a57381b4aca","tid":326074,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41d463ecc7b4fc0bf6ab404224f726d1adea4f8","tid":326074,"uid":46151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:25:22.000Z","msg":"第一 三條問題幾好<br />\n第二條...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該好老尷"},{"pid":"b3785cd4e316aae56149c43659ba55a47f04c825","tid":326074,"uid":73266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:26:48.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c5910b39c71536444fc2ebe248f565b05189eb","tid":326074,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:27:40.000Z","msg":"正皮咗"},{"pid":"42ef28808161a8232de0335c73f65fe729918d70","tid":326074,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一 三條問題幾好<br />\n第二條...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該好老尷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nklopp 心諗：陳婉婷？ 冇人識你wor"},{"pid":"49cccb5c79af497def6c70a542ebf5b5e2282fb2","tid":326074,"uid":59408,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主 英文plz</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港作為細城巿，面對中超崛起，香港足球應該點發展落去？<br />\n你係多仔嗰時，用好少錢就打底拜仁，資源少嘅時候，對球會最重要係乜？香港點先可以同中超鬥呢？<br />\n<br />\nAs a small city, how can Hong Kong Football remain competitive in Asia? Given the rise of the Chinese Super League, what can we do when we can't compete with them financially? We know that you've achieved amazing results with Dortmund against Bayern under a relatively small budget, what is the key of beating the heavy weights when you have little resources?<br />\n<br />\n2. 問下佢知唔知香港嘅陳婉婷係全世界第一個女教練贏男子聯賽，<br />\n但係佢今年佢聯賽、亞冠都失利，你執教緬恩思同多仔都面對過好多高低起跌，你會有咩建議比佢呢？<br />\n<br />\nDo you know Hong Kong has the the World's first woman football coach to win a top-flight men's league? Her name is Chan Yuen Ting and she is coaching Eastern FC, but this year she didn't do well in the HK Premier League and had lots of upsets in the Asian Champions League, including a 7-nil defeat by Phil Scolari's Guangzhou. We know that you have been through lots of ups and downs throughout the years of Mainz and Dortmund, what advice would you give to her?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 利記咁多年嚟，從來都未有過一位亞洲球員，<br />\n你之前同香川合作過喎，你點睇亞洲球員？<br />\n利記幾時有會第一個亞洲球員？<br />\n<br />\nWe know this year is the 125th anniversary of Liverpool, but throughout all these years, there's never been any Asian player in Liverpool entire history. We've seen Asian players doing well in the Premier League, Park with Man United, Son with Spurs. And you yourself have worked with Kagawa before, what are your views on Asian players? When do you think Liverpool will have the first Asian player for the first team? Will it be under your tenure?"},{"pid":"b46a739df5416486495183482b3dbb4527eae9e8","tid":326074,"uid":34572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"唔計英唔英文，其實香港係好少體育記者，因為喺香港係冇得主修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea11d6e5bbfa6f806a01b08081d2039f74eb7ddd","tid":326074,"uid":30186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650ff8a22686753345427c4e3d46f2ce4ebdd8d9","tid":326074,"uid":13088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔計英唔英文，其實香港係好少體育記者，因為喺香港係冇得主修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾部門<br />\n有心做就冇人賞識"},{"pid":"25b99c0d455d66f91bddb48d2c8b0507b0617861","tid":326074,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一 三條問題幾好<br />\n第二條...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該好老尷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nklopp 心諗：陳婉婷？ 冇人識你wor</blockquote><br />\n我都估會咁，但係香港足球近年最威水真係得牛丸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問啲同香港有關嘅仲有咩？"},{"pid":"9aadb0af3fe364cf829071cb312893319d41b766","tid":326074,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"所以呢d記者會應該由官方搞你問我答用live<br />\n咁記者都廢鳩事請 影兩張相咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網友問得仲好過d so call專業既記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d1059d29398fae769d0d615e67a83ec1ffc8ad","tid":326074,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌晒上面鬧記者既人<br />\n<br />\n上一代班廢老死都唔肯退<br />\n新仔點做啊？<br />\n新仔有知識既邊有機會做呢的位啊<br />\n<br />\n但未講香港體記圍威喂人工低</blockquote><br />\n你講得啱，所以真係好欣賞「體路」嗰班人！"},{"pid":"8c18ef02f6437c2ad81e8afb5e8f2da7740e9c1b","tid":326074,"uid":57456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"中學presentation都會練好先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家訪問緊一個世界級既教練，都唔做好準備，唔一早背到滾瓜爛熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲係記者既基本責任掛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744a24b791578c48c40f9c698ab45c1179e61eed","tid":326074,"uid":52855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"高質，支持！"},{"pid":"4bc8f817