ote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港作為細城巿，面對中超崛起，香港足球應該點發展落去？<br />\n你係多仔嗰時，用好少錢就打底拜仁，資源少嘅時候，對球會最重要係乜？香港點先可以同中超鬥呢？<br />\n<br />\nAs a small city, how can Hong Kong Football remain competitive in Asia? Given the rise of the Chinese Super League, what can we do when we can't compete with them financially? We know that you've achieved amazing results with Dortmund against Bayern under a relatively small budget, what is the key of beating the heavy weights when you have little resources?<br />\n<br />\n2. 問下佢知唔知香港嘅陳婉婷係全世界第一個女教練贏男子聯賽，<br />\n但係佢今年佢聯賽、亞冠都失利，你執教緬恩思同多仔都面對過好多高低起跌，你會有咩建議比佢呢？<br />\n<br />\nDo you know Hong Kong has the the World's first woman football coach to win a top-flight men's league? Her name is Chan Yuen Ting and she is coaching Eastern FC, but this year she didn't do well in the HK Premier League and had lots of upsets in the Asian Champions League, including a 7-nil defeat by Phil Scolari's Guangzhou. We know that you have been through lots of ups and downs throughout the years of Mainz and Dortmund, what advice would you give to her?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 利記咁多年嚟，從來都未有過一位亞洲球員，<br />\n你之前同香川合作過喎，你點睇亞洲球員？<br />\n利記幾時有會第一個亞洲球員？<br />\n<br />\nWe know this year is the 125th anniversary of Liverpool, but throughout all these years, there's never been any Asian player in Liverpool entire history. We've seen Asian players doing well in the Premier League, Park with Man United, Son with Spurs. And you yourself have worked with Kagawa before, what are your views on Asian players? When do you think Liverpool will have the first Asian player for the first team? Will it be under your tenure?</blockquote><br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6f7bd08c252248af24c47f57a725291b334814","tid":326074,"uid":65275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T21:27:51.000Z","msg":"讀書叻班人點會做記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675a6afa200685b67285b2caf0eb775bcc6b